      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Real world usage:_ TextEditor, PhotoSHop -> wherevere we need undo and execute feature we need the COmmand Design Pattern\nAnother example is keyboard shortcuts, where ever we need a command like currently this object doing this in future i want this to do something else just like \nremote button currently one button increase volume in future i want it to change the channgle then we use comand\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Real world usage:_ TextEditor, PhotoSHop -> wherevere we need undo and execute feature we need the COmmand Design Pattern\nAnother example is keyboard shortcuts, where ever we need a command like currently this object doing this in future i want this to do something else just like \nremote button currently one button increase volume in future i want it to change the channgle then we use comand\n",
